1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,200
Most AI in games is just a chat box. It talks.

2
00:00:04,200 --> 00:00:06,800
Bob doesn't talk. Bob plays.

3
00:00:06,800 --> 00:00:09,570
You just talk to it — in plain words.

4
00:00:09,570 --> 00:00:13,930
A language model plans. A state machine executes.

5
00:00:13,930 --> 00:00:18,030
It back-chains everything: wood, stone, ore, furnace.

6
00:00:18,030 --> 00:00:22,100
Then it dives to the diamond layer — on real terrain.

7
00:00:22,100 --> 00:00:26,470
Seals lava. Walls off mobs. Recovers its gear.

8
00:00:26,470 --> 00:00:30,200
You say it. It does it. And it keeps getting sharper.

9
00:00:30,200 --> 00:00:32,700
Made by zuuzii
